# Changelog

## [1.2.0] - 2026-03-25

### Security Testing

- Improved map marker interactions
- Added auto and visibility refresh
- Added row filter input
- Added recurrence fields to event form
- Added support for multi calendars through macro parameter
- Added crosshair highlighting

## [1.1.0] - 2026-02-24

### Pre-Security Testing

- Added Put/Delete Requests
- Added linking between sibling events (same event across multi resources)
- Added editing for entire event rucurrence series
- Added display name in "Creator" field for new events
- Updated Form UI, including selecting resources by phase or cluster
- Removed general context to only load dependencies to pages with macro

## [1.0.0] - 2026-01-23

### Initial release

- Map + scheduler macro
- Read-only integration with Team Calendar
